projects.title: Teleoperation of Kuka YouBot in CoppeliaSim (V-Rep) and Matlab
projects.description: Developed a program to remotely operate a Kuka YouBot from Matlab to CoppeliaSim (robotic simulation software).

projects.title: Object Retrieval from Grid-Based Forest using a Multi-Agent System
projects.description: Developed using AgentSpeak on the JASON platform, I developed a multi-agent system with the aim of one agent being able to traverse a forest and retrive items based on conditions, and a second agent to make counter-decisions based on certain actions from the first agent.

projects.title: Receipe Website
projects.description: Worked on a group project to develop a website where a user could browse, search, favourite, and log in to view a range of recipes based on a MySQL database.

projects.title: Behaviour-Based Map Building Robot in CoppeliaSim (V-Rep)
projects.description: Collaborated on a group project to develop a map-building robot in CoppeliaSim and Matlab.
